title: Aggregation of WITS, IED Attacks in Afghanistan, 1st qtr 1.1.2010-3.31.2010 into Geo-referencing of Ethnic Groups, Afghanistan
name: Aggregation of WITS, IED Attacks in Afghanistan, 1st qtr 1.1.2010-3.31.2010 into Geo-referencing of Ethnic Groups, Afghanistan
description: IED attacks pulled from the Worldwide Incidents Tracking System from the Q2 of 2009. Data includes number of deaths, wounded, and hostages taken in each attack as well as a text description and location. Sum values were calculated by aggregating the values of each attribute into the ethnic areas of Afghanistan.

properties.G1LONGNAM: Pamir Tajiks: Yazghulems, Bartangs, Roshanis, Shugnanis, Vakhanis, Ishkashimis, Badzhui, Khuf, Sarykolese, Sanglechis, Munjanis
